o\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mikael Dalle, a 53-year-old local out with his son, said he was bothered by the illegal hawkers who shout out to passers-by, offering unlicensed food and drinks, trinkets and berets.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mikael_of_Wollo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.510930480903934e-12, \"text\": \"Mikael\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mikael_of_Wollo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mikael_of_Wollo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"the illegal hawkers\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"passers\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"unlicensed food\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"drinks\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"trinkets\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"berets\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has definitely got worse, and we have lived around here for the last eight years,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last eight years\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around seven million people ascend the Eiffel Tower each year, and many more pose for photos, have picnics or play ball games in the Champ-de-Mars.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around seven million people\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"many more pose\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"picnics\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"ball games\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"the Champ-de\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"Mars\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With so many visitors, the park's lawns are often rubbed bare, while at night, they are strewn with rubbish left by revellers.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many visitors\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"the park's lawns\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"rubbish\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"revellers\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You should see it at six in the morning.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is catastrophic,\\\" said a 53-year-old dog walker, Louis, who declined to give his surname.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 53-year-old dog walker\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"Louis\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"his surname\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leftover food and overflowing bins are a delight for the flourishing rat population.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leftover food and overflowing bins\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"a delight\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"the flourishing rat population\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Construction works are held for the beach volleyball competition in Champ-de-Mars, in preparation for Olympic Summer games, near Eiffel Tower in Paris.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2708, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.771196350654786e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped