", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"the dark\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"Louis\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The right-wing opponents of Socialist Mayor Anne Hidalgo blame her for the problems, with local senator Agnes Evren claiming the area has turned into \\\"the far West\\\".\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3064, \"end\": 3076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The right-wing opponents\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"the problems\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"local senator Agnes Evren\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"the far West\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the tower's workers are unhappy, launching a five-day strike in February to protest against its state of disrepair and demanding the city spend more on painting and anti-rust protection.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the tower's workers\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"a five-day strike\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"its state\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"disrepair\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"painting\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-rust protection\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Hidalgo, an eco-minded left-winger re-elected for a second term in 2020, is admired by many for her policies to restrict cars and promote 